Synopsis:

At the reality show, Bass, a male movie superstar was surprised the former high school beauty queen, Namkaang (that he was dreamed about) turned into heavyweight woman. The audiences loved the new jumbo queen and she became a new sensation movie star. In order to keep his rating high, he tries to win her heart.
Is she will fall into his trap or still remember someone still love and care about her at home?
